(a) The Bank’s claims in their entirety fell within the scope of the Tribunal’s jurisdiction;   
(b) The Employer’s demands were valid;   
(c) The Bank shall pay AED 160,722,046 to the Employer plus simple interest at the rate of $4 \%$ above the Bank’s offi cial lending rate from 1 October 2020;   
(d) The Bank shall pay the Employer’s legal costs in the sum of AED 1,746,806.25 and arbitration costs in the sum of AED 362,292.84 plus simple interest at the rate of $1 \%$ above the Bank's offi cial lending rate.
